astian_Bach\", \"score\": 0.9999986179364442, \"rank\": 1.3820655458179587e-06, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We do not like this uncertainty.\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 549, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We do not like it for the overall situation for nobody.\", \"from\": 550, \"to\": 605, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So, we would be more than pleased to look into it,\\\" he continued.\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 673, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But what is not possible is that somebody is saying, you know, 'this is not a woman' just by looking at somebody or by falling prey to a defamation campaign by not a credible organization.\\\"\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 864, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"IOC is gaslighting the world.\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 895, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 866, \"end\": 869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.8894068255356855e-18, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bach says there is no solid scientific way to tell who is a woman!\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 962, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 896, \"end\": 900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 0.9999986179364442, \"rank\": 1.3820655458179587e-06, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is taking us all for fools.pic.twitter.com/imUGgwnTv3  - FairPlayForWomen (@fairplayw